*"Uz velike zahvalnosti* se zahvaljujemo svim donatorima koji su pomogli u realizaciji projekta." (We would like to express our great gratitude to all donors who helped to realize this project.)

*"Mnoga sredstva su obezbeđena uz zahvalnosti* našim partnerima." (Many resources were made available thanks to our partners.)

*"Naša zahvalnost* je beskrajna za one koji su nam pomogli u teškim vremenima." (Our gratitude is endless for those who helped us in difficult times.)

*"Ovom prilikom izražavamo svoju zahvalnosti* našim prijateljima." (We would like to express our gratitude to our friends on this occasion.)

*"Ona je iskazala veliku zahvalnosti* njenim roditeljima za sve što su uradili." (She expressed great gratitude to her parents for all they have done.)